<title>USA: Avatex Corp skips quarterly div on pref shrs.</title>
<headline>Avatex Corp skips quarterly div on pref shrs.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Avatex Corp said Wednesday it would skip its quarterly dividend payments scheduled for July</p>
<p>The company said it would not pay dividends on its $5.00 cumulative convertible preferred stock and on $4.20 cumulative exchangeable series A preferred stock. A company official was not available for comment.</p>
<p>Avatex Corp's stock traded unchanged at 1-1/8 Wednesday afternoon.</p>
